---
name: get_capped_campaigns
description: >
  Returns Google Ads campaigns that are losing impression share because their
  daily budget is too low (capped). Reports each campaign's daily budget,
  30-day spend, percentage of impressions lost, estimated missed conversions,
  and the recommended budget to remove the cap. Use this when the user asks
  about capped campaigns, budget constraints, or missed conversions in
  Google Ads.
---
Use the omni-assistant variant for chat; the gap-finder/growth-engine agents
use identify_budget_constraints (an unscoped variant) instead.
